                    <title>IMHO coderetreat is about try…</title>
                    <link rel="alternate" href="http://coderetreat.org/xn/detail/6456126:Comment:22170"/>
                                        <id>tag:coderetreat.org,2013-04-17:6456126:Comment:22170</id>
                                        <updated>2013-04-17T14:44:47.444Z</updated>
                    
                                            <author>
                            <name>Valdis Pornieks</name>
                            <uri>http://coderetreat.org/profile/ValdisPornieks</uri>
                        </author>
                    
                    <summary type="html">
                        &lt;p&gt;IMHO coderetreat is about trying out things and learning from the group based on the experience gained in the trial. Therefore it&#039;s important to get the participants to really evaluate their approach to the problem and compare it to what others have done. That will improve learning from the group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Try to identify differences between teams approaches, excel them and engage the teams to take part in the discussion. Also look for blockers, where teams had difficulties and involve the…&lt;/p&gt;                    </summary>

                                            <content type="html">
                            &lt;p&gt;IMHO coderetreat is about trying out things and learning from the group based on the experience gained in the trial. Therefore it&#039;s important to get the participants to really evaluate their approach to the problem and compare it to what others have done. That will improve learning from the group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Try to identify differences between teams approaches, excel them and engage the teams to take part in the discussion. Also look for blockers, where teams had difficulties and involve the group in coming up with possible solutions. This might give you also ideas on what constraints to better use in the next session&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;cite&gt;Konrad Malewski said:&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote cite=&quot;http://coderetreat.org/forum/topics/question-on-final-retrospective?groupUrl=facilitators&amp;amp;commentId=6456126%3AComment%3A22348&amp;amp;xg_source=msg_com_gr_forum#6456126Comment22348&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;xg_user_generated&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;What about retrospective between sessions ? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;cite&gt; &lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;                        </content>
                    
