                    <summary type="html">
                        &lt;p&gt;I usually have everyone stand in a circle and we go around with everyone answering the three questions. This way it&#039;s more of a peer sharing exercise, and I find the interaction is good.&lt;/p&gt;                    </summary>

                                            <content type="html">
                            &lt;p&gt;I usually have everyone stand in a circle and we go around with everyone answering the three questions. This way it&#039;s more of a peer sharing exercise, and I find the interaction is good.&lt;/p&gt;                        </content>
                    
